T1  - Markov Perfect Equilibrium Advertising Strategies of Lanchester Duopoly Model: A Technical Note
AU  - Jarrar, Ramla
AU  - Martín-Herrán, Guiomar
AU  - Zaccour, Georges
Y1  - 2004/07/01
